HR 347 Original 2026 Regular Session Braud
Urges and requests that the Dept. of Transportation and Development (DOTD) study the
feasibility and benefits of establishing uniform toll signage, toll dispute procedures, and toll
customer service centers at all toll facilities within a certain radius. Requires the DOTD to
submit a written report detailing its findings to the House transportation committee before
Feb. 1, 2027.
